The paper discusses the development and implementation of a recommender system for academic products, specifically research articles, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR). The system also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and data mining (cs.DM). The paper also mentions the use of open source software and the goal of facilitating research, which could fall under the categories of cyberinfrastructure (cs.CY) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
